EcoSense Receives Funding from Bain Capital for LED Lighting

-- B y   A n d r e w   H e r n d o n
-- 
2011-10-18T22:07:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/ecosense-receives-funding-from-bain-capital-for-led-lighting.html
EcoSense Lighting Inc., a closely
held provider of energy-efficient LED fixtures, received $13
million in venture capital financing led by  Bain Capital 
Ventures.  EcoSense disclosed the Series B funding in a filing today.
It will use the money to develop its light-emitting diode
products and hire more engineers and salespeople, the New York-
based company said in a statement on its website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrew Herndon in  San Francisco  at 
 aherndon2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
